      <title>美国批准为沙特阿拉伯提供 10 亿美元的新军事训练</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/us-approves-1-billion-in-new-military-training-for-saudi-arabia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院批准为沙特阿拉伯提供 10 亿美元的军事训练，更新了一项加深两个合作伙伴之间关系的计划，同时仍然坚持禁止销售某些进攻性武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/us-approves-1-billion-in-new-military-training-for-saudi-arabia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 20:45:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国表示红海巡逻队将能够挫败胡塞武装袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/us-says-red-sea-highway-patrol-able-to-thwart-houthi-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼发言人表示，美国新的国际海军联盟将充当“高速公路巡逻队”，保护红海航运免受伊朗支持的胡塞武装分子的袭击，尽管它不会为个别船只护航。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/us-says-red-sea-highway-patrol-able-to-thwart-houthi-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 20:15:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在竞选混乱中，德桑蒂斯的支持转向新的超级政治行动委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/desantis-support-shifts-to-new-super-pacs-amid-campaign-tumult</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最近几周，与佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 结盟的两个新的超级政治行动委员会预订了超过 800 万美元的广告，以推动他的总统竞选，而几个月来一直支持他竞选的组织“永不退缩”(Never Back Down) 在内部动荡中削减了广告支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/desantis-support-shifts-to-new-super-pacs-amid-campaign-tumult</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 19:33:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院拒绝快速审理特朗普豁免冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/supreme-court-refuses-to-put-trump-immunity-clash-on-fast-track</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院拒绝立即决定前总统唐纳德·特朗普是否因寻求推翻 2020 年选举失败而免受起诉，这对检察官于 3 月 4 日开始审判的努力造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/supreme-court-refuses-to-put-trump-immunity-clash-on-fast-track</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 19:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称他不是希特勒的“学生”，为反移民言论辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/trump-says-he-s-no-hitler-student-defends-anti-migrant-remark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他不是阿道夫·希特勒的“学生”，并为他对无证移民的评论进行了辩护，批评者将这些评论与纳粹领导人对犹太人的评论进行了比较。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/trump-says-he-s-no-hitler-student-defends-anti-migrant-remark</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 18:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其下周将瑞典的北约申办重新列入议程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/turkish-lawmakers-put-sweden-s-nato-bid-back-on-agenda-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其议会委员会将于下周恢复有关瑞典加入北约申请的讨论，从而将瑞典的批准重新提上议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/turkish-lawmakers-put-sweden-s-nato-bid-back-on-agenda-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 18:15:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
