      <title>联合国安理会通过增加加沙援助决议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/un-security-council-passes-resolution-on-increasing-gaza-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国安理会周五通过一项决议，呼吁增加对加沙地带的援助，但没有要求以色列和哈马斯停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/un-security-council-passes-resolution-on-increasing-gaza-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 17:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委员会表示，刚果将于年底前任命下一任总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/congo-to-celebrate-new-year-with-next-president-commission-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国选举委员会将于周五开始公布该国 12 月 20 日的民意调查结果，计划在年底前宣布下一任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/congo-to-celebrate-new-year-with-next-president-commission-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 15:06:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
